---
title: Cognitive Attractor State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> FLEXIBLE: Default state

    FOCUSED: Stable attractor, deep well, low noise
    FLEXIBLE: Shallow attractors, easy switching
    CHAOTIC: No stable attractor, high noise, exploration
    CONSOLIDATING: Sleep-like, offline integration

    FLEXIBLE --> FOCUSED: Task engagement
    FOCUSED --> FLEXIBLE: Task complete

    FLEXIBLE --> CHAOTIC: High uncertainty
    CHAOTIC --> FLEXIBLE: Pattern found

    FLEXIBLE --> CONSOLIDATING: Idle timeout
    FOCUSED --> CONSOLIDATING: Natural break
    CHAOTIC --> CONSOLIDATING: Exhaustion

    CONSOLIDATING --> FLEXIBLE: Wake signal
